{"tid":1433649,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"講開機管局，仲有冇人記得呢部陰濕野?","createTime":"2019-08-08T14:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T14:52:13.000Z","uid":298034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"437d27b563f180fbd6da8038a9c56f52823af6c3","tid":1433649,"uid":298034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:10:39.000Z","msg":"唔係新野，但既然講開機管局表示離境大堂都要出示Passport同機票，我就拎返出黎俾大家參考下。<br />\n<br />\n下圖係根據「機場自助保安閘口－個人資料收集聲明」整理嘅簡化版。歡迎指出錯漏及作出補充。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongairport.com/tc/passenger-guide/airport-security/e-security-gates-privacy-policy.page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongairport.com%2Ftc%2Fpassenger-guide%2Fairport-security%2Fe-security-gates-privacy-policy.page&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Uzob1WjLKDnR9IVaUJYWuI%3D&h=7e583d27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongairport.com/tc/passenger-guide/airport-security/e-security-gates-privacy-policy.page</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TkwPgGv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTkwPgGv.jpg&h=49b8c92c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解有問題？請睇&darr;<br />\n《視點31》【新疆監控通道曝光，監控趨勢延伸本港？】（RTHK31：16/4/2019）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dh4Su3zvRDU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdh4Su3zvRDU&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Uzob1WjLKDnR9IVaUJYWuI%3D&h=bcc424a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dh4Su3zvRDU</a><br />\n<br />\n我都想行輔助通道同佢講唔俾佢收集個人資料就冇事，<br />\n但人地話點都要影，唔通你到時同機管局嘈咩。<br />\n人地話OK，但個鏡頭又對住你，影咗都唔知啦。<br />\nPassport又要俾佢過機，佢真係唔收集，定係廢事煩照正常程序過機，冇人知。"},{"pid":"a53f9d0836a74ef6fc9b1f972686884126da6eb8","tid":1433649,"uid":58958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:52:13.000Z","msg":"試過係可以拒絕"}]}